    • getVersion

      MemberVersion getVersion()
      Returns the Hazelcast codebase version of this member; this may or may not be different from the version reported by Cluster.getClusterVersion(), for example when a node with a different codebase version is added to an existing cluster. See the documentation for Cluster.getClusterVersion() for a more thorough discussion of Cluster and Member / Node version.
      Returns:
      the MemberVersion of this member.
      Since:
      3.8
